  <zone type="main">
    <line><add><ptr target="c57-0039.01"/></add>These questions continually recurred but I </line>
    <line>was unable to solve them.</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>The volume of Plutarchs lives which I</line>
    <line>possessed contained the histories of the first</line>
    <line>founders of the ancient republics &#x2014; This book</line>
    <line>had a far different effect upon me from</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">the letters Sorrows</del> the letters of Werter. I lea<add
        place="superlinear">r</add>ned</line>
    <line>from <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">that</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs"><del rend="strikethrough">his</del> Werter's <del
            rend="strikethrough">g</del> imaginations</add>
      </mod> despondency &amp; gloom; but Plutarch</line>
    <line>taught me high thoughts &#x2014; he elevated me abov</line>e <line><del
        rend="strikethrough">m</del> the wretched sphere of my own reflections</line>
    <line>to admire &amp; love the heroes of past ages. <del rend="strikethrough">Yet</del></line>
    <line>Many things I read surpassed my unterstanding</line>
    <line>and <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">knowledge</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">experience</add>
      </mod> I had a very <del rend="double-strike">t</del> confused know</line>
    <line>ledge of kingdoms &amp; wide extents of country</line>
    <line>mighty river and boundless seas! But I</line>
    <line>was perfectly unacquainted with towns &amp; <del rend="smear">was</del></line>
    <line>large <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">assemblegs</del>
        <add place="superlinear">assemblages</add>
      </mod> of men. The cottage<mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">rs</del>
        <add place="superlinear">of my protectors</add>
        <del rend="strikethrough">were</del>
        <add><del rend="strikethrough">was</del></add>
        <add place="sublinear">
          <del rend="strikethrough"><!--requires restore encoding, see scholar's note-->had been</del></add>
      </mod>
    </line>
    <line>the <del rend="double-strike">o</del> only school <add place="intralinear" resp="#pbs"
        >in</add>
      <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">where</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">which</add>
      </mod> I <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">had</add> studied human</line>
    <line>nature &#x2014; But this book <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">threw a new light</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">upon</del>
        <metamark>&#x2038;</metamark>
        <add place="superlinear">developed new &amp; mightier scenes of action</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">it</del> I read of men concerned in public</line>
    <line>affairs governing <del rend="strikethrough">their species &#x2014;</del>
      <del rend="strikethrough">an</del> or masser</line>
    <line>cering their speceis. I felt the greatest ardour</line>
    <line>for virtue rise within me and abhor</line>
    <line>rence for vice <del rend="scribble"><unclear>f</unclear></del> as far as I understood <del
        rend="strikethrough">it</del> the</line>
    <line>signification of those terms relative as they</line>
    <line>were <del rend="strikethrough">only</del>, as I applied them, to pleasure</line>
    <line>and pain <mod type="additions">
        <del rend="strikethrough">with</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">alone. Induced by</add>
      </mod> these feelings <del rend="strikethrough">it may be</del></line>
    <line>I was of course led to admire peacable</line>
    <line>lawgivers Numa, Solon &amp; Lycurgus more than</line>
    <line>Romulus and Theseus. The patriarchal lives</line>
    <line>of my protectors <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">induced</del>
        <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough">im</del> caused</add>
      </mod>
      <del rend="strikethrough">to a greater degree</del></line>
    <line>these impressions <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">to take a firm hold on my mind</add>
      </mod> &#x2014; perhaps if my first <delSpan spanTo="#c57-0039.02" rend="strikethrough"
      />resid</line>
    <line>ence<anchor xml:id="c57-0039.02"/><add><ptr target="#c57-0039.03"/></add> had been <mod>
        <mod type="additions" resp="#pbs">
          <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
          <add place="superlinear">made</add>
        </mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">with</del>
        <add place="superlinear">by</add>
      </mod> a young soldier burning</line>
  </zone>
